creator: Bumblebee Digital
descriptionHtml:
Shikara, an authentic Indian restaurant located in the heart of Clarkson and Mindarie offers a unique, modern Indian dining experience. We are one of the most upscale restaurant yet very affordable and due to this we have become the major eating joint in the area.

Shikara is term which is used to describe “The House Boat”. The house boats are very famous in Jammu & Kashmir and tourists from all over the world are attracted by the charm of staying on a houseboat.

With more than three decades of of experience in preparing Indian food, our chefs know the importance of the unique spices and tastes of authentic Indian ingredients. They are continuously evolving with changing times so that you get the real blend of the Indian food.

Come enjoy our delicious authentic Indian food with unmatched hospitality and have an exquisite dining experience.
